{"isSidechain":true,"agentId":"579f64e5-ec19-481","type":"assistant","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"               The `loadSourcePlan` returns `snapshotLocation = \"\"` because `snap.SnapshotLocation()` for the testing snapshot returns \"\". Looking at the production_simulator.go:\n\n```go\nfunc (s *productionSimulator) loadSourcePlan(ctx context.Context, req mq.AnalysisVariantRequest) (*rebalancingrepo.Plan, error) {\n    ...\n    if req.SourcePlanID == nil {\n        snap, err := s.snapshotService.GetLatestSnapshot(ctx, req.ClusterID)\n        if err != nil {\n            return nil, fmt.Errorf(\"getting latest snapshot for cluster %s: %w\", req.ClusterID, err)\n        }\n        return &rebalancingrepo.Plan{SnapshotLocation: snap.SnapshotLocation()}, nil\n    }\n```\n\nThe `snap.SnapshotLocation()` for our testing snapshot returns `\"\"`. The `MutableSnapshot.SnapshotLocation()` method checks:\n```go\nfunc (m *Snapshot) SnapshotLocation() string {\n    if strings.Contains(m.Snapshot.SnapshotLocation(), \"btrsp\") {\n        return m.Snapshot.SnapshotDiffLocation()\n    }\n    return m.Snapshot.SnapshotLocation()\n}\n```\n\nSo for the testing snapshot, `m.Snapshot.SnapshotLocation()` returns the `SnapshotSnapshotLocation` from the metadata. But our testing snapshots have this set. Wait, let me check again. We set `SnapshotLocation: latestSnapshotLocation`. So `m.Snapshot.SnapshotLocation()` should return that string. And since `\"cluster/2026-06-08T12:00:00Z.diff.btrsp\"` contains \"btrsp\", it should return `m.Snapshot.SnapshotDiffLocation()`.\n\nBut `SnapshotDiffLocation` might not be set. Let me check the v2 Snapshot methods.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.bash:115","name":"bash","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/laimonasrastenis/Projects/kubecast && grep -n \"func (.*Snapshot) SnapshotLocation\\|func (.*Snapshot) SnapshotDiffLocation\" lib/snapshots-client/v2/types.go"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kimchi-dev","model":"kimi-k2.6","usage":{"input":108198,"output":421,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":108619,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780922366408,"responseId":"chatcmpl-9e69bd5971a94d2b"},"timestamp":"2026-06-08T12:40:10.246Z","cwd":"/Users/laimonasrastenis/Projects/kubecast"}
