{"isSidechain":true,"agentId":"579f64e5-ec19-481","type":"assistant","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"                    Now I understand. `MutableSnapshot.SnapshotLocation()` checks if `\"btrsp\"` is in `m.Snapshot.SnapshotLocation()`. If so, it returns `m.Snapshot.SnapshotDiffLocation()`. But `SnapshotDiffLocation` is empty in our testing snapshots.\n\nI need to set `SnapshotDiffLocation` as well, or set the location differently. For v2 `.diff.btrsp` snapshots, the `SnapshotLocation` should be the full path and `SnapshotDiffLocation` should probably be the same. Actually, looking at how the service works:\n\nIn `loadSourcePlan`, it calls `snap.SnapshotLocation()` which for a real `.diff.btrsp` snapshot would return... hmm, let me trace this.\n\nA real MutableSnapshot wrapping a v2 snapshot with `SnapshotLocation = \"gs://bucket/cluster/2026-05-28T13:46:41.662318111Z.diff.btrsp\"`:\n\n1. `m.Snapshot.SnapshotLocation()` returns `\"gs://bucket/cluster/2026-05-28T13:46:41.662318111Z.diff.btrsp\"` (contains \"btrsp\")\n2. Returns `m.Snapshot.SnapshotDiffLocation()`\n\nBut what does `SnapshotDiffLocation()` return? I need to understand the actual data model.\n\nLooking at `TestingSnapshotMetadata`:\n```go\nSnapshotLocation     string\nSnapshotDiffLocation string\n```\n\nFor a diff (v2) snapshot, the `SnapshotLocation` might be the base/older snapshot and `SnapshotDiffLocation` is the diff snapshot itself. Or they might be the same.\n\nLet me just set `SnapshotDiffLocation` to the same value to avoid the issue.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.edit:117","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/laimonasrastenis/Projects/kubecast/services/autoscaler/internal/services/clusteradvisor/executor/production_simulator_test.go","edits":[{"oldText":"func newTestSnapshot(clusterID uuid.UUID, location string) *snapshots.Snapshot {\n\treturn snapshots.NewMutableSnapshot(snapshots_v2.NewTestingSnapshot(snapshots_v2.TestingSnapshotMetadata{\n\t\tID:               uuid.New(),\n\t\tClusterID:        clusterID,\n\t\tSnapshotLocation: location,\n\t}).Snapshot)\n}","newText":"func newTestSnapshot(clusterID uuid.UUID, location string) *snapshots.Snapshot {\n\treturn snapshots.NewMutableSnapshot(snapshots_v2.NewTestingSnapshot(snapshots_v2.TestingSnapshotMetadata{\n\t\tID:                   uuid.New(),\n\t\tClusterID:            clusterID,\n\t\tSnapshotLocation:     location,\n\t\tSnapshotDiffLocation: location,\n\t}).Snapshot)\n}"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kimchi-dev","model":"kimi-k2.6","usage":{"input":108852,"output":580,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":109432,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780922430927,"responseId":"chatcmpl-b40261309c590fcf"},"timestamp":"2026-06-08T12:41:52.432Z","cwd":"/Users/laimonasrastenis/Projects/kubecast"}
